Overview

This dashboard shows Breach Record overview related to the SpyCloud Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested breach records from SpyCloud.

It showcases the aggregate count of IP addresses, email accounts, usernames, and exposed passwords. It shows the breakdown of breach records by publish date and severity. The dashboard also includes the top 10 exposed plaintext passwords, the top 10 emails, the top 10 usernames, the top 10 domains, and the top 10 IP Addresses. It also highlights the 10 most infected emails, the 10 most infected usernames, the 10 most infected operating systems, top 10 infected devices and the top 10 infected target subdomains. In addition, it illustrates the infected device details. By default, it fetches new records every day.
